  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Launch & Loot\" is a rogue-lite dungeon crawler with vibrant pixel art, where each room is procedurally generated. Use the environment to your advantage by throwing objects and loot to defeat enemies. Discover unique power-ups that change your playstyle with every run!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Potion Launches!!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Different effects on items</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252420/extras/bbd9675e9d4ac01002d36896d04d9fb6.poster.avif?t=1735329064\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252420/extras/bbd9675e9d4ac01002d36896d04d9fb6.webm?t=1735329064\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252420/extras/bbd9675e9d4ac01002d36896d04d9fb6.mp4?t=1735329064\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Power-Ups</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >100 Scenarios</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >40 Items</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252420/extras/c35c79dd29052be5b2bfe0a9c6b424a7.avif?t=1735329064\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252420/extras_big/c35c79dd29052be5b2bfe0a9c6b424a7.avif?t=1735329064 width=800 height=258 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252420/extras/a1eeec0040b88d8cd6fd9c2ab0653f69.poster.avif?t=1735329064\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252420/extras/a1eeec0040b88d8cd6fd9c2ab0653f69.webm?t=1735329064\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252420/extras/a1eeec0040b88d8cd6fd9c2ab0653f69.mp4?t=1735329064\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Boss Fights</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252420/extras/061402a27192acb607b3684dc8c9bef2.poster.avif?t=1735329064\" width=692 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252420/extras/061402a27192acb607b3684dc8c9bef2.webm?t=1735329064\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252420/extras/061402a27192acb607b3684dc8c9bef2.mp4?t=1735329064\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Other Features:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrade Builds</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Special Power-Ups</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Procedural Generation</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Various Levels</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Alternative Stages</p></li></ul>",
